long_desc.thetext:
Seems to be a problem concerning the loading order of classes, that has been introduced by the refactoring related to bug 6665.
The refactoring has introduced a new environment-setting called "ecmascript.array.indexof":

qx.Bootstrap.define("qx.bom.client.EcmaScript",
{
  defer : function(statics) {
    // array polyfill
    qx.core.Environment.add("ecmascript.array.indexof", statics.getArrayIndexOf);


The problem is that no other class references the class "qx.bom.client.EcmaScript". Therefore this class is never loaded by our javascript loading mechnism, and therefore the environment "ecmascript.array.indexof" is never set.
